name: Library Level Build 2
description:
This is the second build to Daniel T's Library level.

INSTRUCTIONS FOR GAMEPLAY:

*NOTE: FOR MY LEVEL, PRESS THE ESC BUTTON TO PAUSE THE GAME*

*PAUSE THE GAME FROM THE START OF THE GAME, CLICK TO INTERACT WITH THE BUTTONS*

*PRESS ESC TO GO BACK TO THE GAME ITSELF*

*ORIGINAL MOVEMENT IS THE "WASD" KEYS BUT IN MENU YOU CAN CHANGE DIRECTIONAL KEYS AND INTERACT KEYS*
